OL,6,F"When prices for food and energy were
OL,7,Fincreasing, we saw people cut back and
OL,8,Fmake changes to their spending and
OL,9,Fshopping habits, but now we're seeing
OL,10,Fthat some major life decisions are
OL,11,Fbeing delayed as people are weighing
OL,12,Fup whether or not they can afford to
OL,13,Fact on the plans they'd made."
