OL,6,FThe UK squeezed more than a decade's
OL,7,Fworth of 'normal' inflation into just
OL,8,Fthree years, according to the
OL,9,FFoundation, which is focused on
OL,10,Fimproving the living standards for
OL,11,Fthose on low to middle incomes.
OL,13,FThe Foundation said that households
OL,14,Fgenerally have cut down sharply on the
OL,15,Famount they consume during the cost-of-
OL,16,Fliving crisis.
